{"tid":2369321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"各區運動場或設濕貨年宵  花農寸政府無腦：和合石搞冇病毒","createTime":"2021-01-17T04:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T05:16:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a47f833db88218db0b50919bbdfda66aafaf2a2d","tid":2369321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/JMOII3SMUFH2BL43ZTWDBLD6C4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FJMOII3SMUFH2BL43ZTWDBLD6C4%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=883167f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FJMOII3SMUFH2BL43ZTWDBLD6C4%2F&h=69bebe0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/JMOII3SMUFH2BL43ZTWDBLD6C4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n各區運動場或設濕貨年宵 <br />\n花農寸政府無腦：和合石搞冇病毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bq4p1CNvVXm_miTtXUCVH1VUma0=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UBFN273ER5GE5OZFAKHU7X45UI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBq4p1CNvVXm_miTtXUCVH1VUma0%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUBFN273ER5GE5OZFAKHU7X45UI.jpg&h=9630dd01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新田信芯園百合花盛放，開放予市民入場參觀及買花，幫補收入。<br />\n<br />\n【武肺第四波】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：許樹昌促禁足配合<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府本月初宣佈取消全港年宵市場，並聲稱會協助花農在各區公共屋邨或其他地點銷售年花，惟事隔逾一周，至今仍未有任何具體細節。有傳媒報道，政府正研究在各區運動場內設立濕貨年宵市場。有花農炮轟政府信口開河，「公共屋邨同運動場搞唔通冇疫情咩？去和合石搞就一定冇啦」。<br />\n<br />\n昨日《經濟日報》引述消息報道，政府正研究改為在全港各區都設置濕貨年宵市場，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：佐敦增兩廈強檢 食肆落閘避疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FD8WJra7Mwi4bAZwB5x2lX3F9X0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JHQL5LKIRRBGNDND3BMUTQIM2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFD8WJra7Mwi4bAZwB5x2lX3F9X0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJHQL5LKIRRBGNDND3BMUTQIM2M.jpg&h=a5995452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府宣佈取消花市，不少市民到千葉園選購蘭花，園方在疫情下亦不敢加價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n桃花大王：唔好信政府<br />\n<br />\n報道以「政府改變態度」形容事態發展，不過根據食環署本月8日發出的新聞稿，宣佈取消各年宵花市的同時，也聲稱「為協助花農以其他方式銷售年花，署方會與業界持份者會面，在防疫抗疫的前提下探討可行措施，例如在各區公共屋邨或其他地點物色合適地方銷售年花，盡量減低取消年宵市場對業界的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n事隔了超過一星期，距離。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「桃花大王」劉海濤則語帶激動說：「唔好信政府呀，佢講之嘛！」。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n元朗信芯園68歲老闆梁日信表示，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n千葉園負責人之一楊尹俊表大呻「好難適應」，不清楚政府有何決策，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n原已在元朗年宵市場租了兩檔的財利（花圃）農場老闆馮正表示，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生：取消晒風險最細<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超認為，舉辦年宵最大問題是各區人潮湧去一個地方聚集，增加染疫風險，「當然取消晒風險係最細」，但會影響經濟和民生，亦要考慮如何協助花農散貨，「屋邨環境唔係咁好，尤其舊屋邨，仲係有疫情」。他認為是否在各區設置濕貨年宵須視乎疫情走勢，「如果疫情平穩，喺室外運動場風險比室內風險細啲」。食環署回覆查詢時對是否在運動場舉辦花市不置可否，僅稱在防疫抗疫前提下，正積極考慮合適方案以協助花農銷售年花，並會透過分散人流及壓縮規模來減低聚眾風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花農血本無歸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HSaqo0NO_f6BA2HhU59YEa38hiA=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DSXF5EIGGJH3JPUBJ5AT2DYBUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHSaqo0NO_f6BA2HhU59YEa38hiA%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDSXF5EIGGJH3JPUBJ5AT2DYBUA.jpg&h=7b6f97e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■信芯園老闆梁日信指花苗成本達七位數，現只盼可收回成本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pYB4r08jJwMPLLoEm0aoraP_-SE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MI5DYDUD6NAITD75U5IK7VPDL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpYB4r08jJwMPLLoEm0aoraP_-SE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMI5DYDUD6NAITD75U5IK7VPDL4.jpg&h=5b8ffcf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■財利（花圃）老闆馮正原在元朗年宵租了兩檔，現時貨向未明。<br />\n<br />\n[img]■千葉園負責人楊尹俊指因年宵取消，已付租金、花苗等成本料蝕300萬元。[/img]<br />\n■千葉園負責人楊尹俊指因年宵取消，已付租金、花苗等成本料蝕300萬元。"},{"pid":"285b5e189853f7acdd330b52ed9c504f8d48e0ad","tid":2369321,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"去和合石搵君君老公"},{"pid":"d956d3df7a51a5bc5e4ada5a1af187168342fb02","tid":2369321,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:14:20.000Z","msg":"花農犯咗國安法"},{"pid":"848ee83752ee63698bc3e015662cce14d13631f8","tid":2369321,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"無曬反對派<br />\n點解都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}